This Python app displays random Kanye West quotes in a simple GUI using the tkinter library. It fetches quotes from the Kanye REST API and updates the text on the screen when the user clicks a button.

Features

Clean GUI with tkinter

Dynamic quote fetching with requests

Interactive button to retrieve new quotes



---

Requirements

Python 3.10+

requests library (can be installed via pip)


pip install requests


